{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/depression-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/depression-and-driving","title":"Depression and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T12:54:04+00:00","details":{"need_id":"2273","business_proposition":false,"description":"You must tell DVLA about your depression if it affects your driving - download the correct form to let them know","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> about your depression if it affects your driving.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to £1,000 if you don’t tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> about a medical condition that affects your driving. If you’re involved in an accident, you may be prosecuted.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Car or motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<p>If you&rsquo;re not sure if your depression affects your driving, check with your doctor. </p>\n\n<p>If it does, you must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form M1 and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form. </p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_066650.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘M1 - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 252KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Bus, coach or lorry licence</h2>\n\n<p>If you&rsquo;re not sure if your depression affects your driving, check with your doctor. </p>\n\n<p>If it does, you must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form M1V and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form. </p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_172725.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download M1V ‘Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 243KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"short_description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null}],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/driving-if-disabled.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/driving-if-disabled","title":"Medical conditions, disabilities and driving","format":"guide","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:10:22+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/health-conditions-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/health-conditions-and-driving","title":"Health conditions and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:13:59+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/giving-up-your-driving-licence.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/giving-up-your-driving-licence","title":"Surrendering your driving licence","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:09:58+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition","title":"Re-apply for a driving licence following a medical condition","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:11:37+00:00"}]}